---
import CustomButton from "./ui/CustomButton.astro";
import CalificationForm from "./opt-in/calificationForm";
---

<section class="py-6 sm:py-8 md:pt-[45px] md:pb-[80px]">
  <img
    class="w-32 sm:w-40 md:w-[180px] mx-auto"
    src="/images/sales-mastery-logo.png"
    alt="Sales Mastery"
  />
  <p
    class="leading-[120%] mt-4 sm:mt-6 md:mt-8 mx-auto text-base md:text-[18px] text-center max-w-[90%] sm:max-w-[500px] text-white/80 px-4"
  >
    +1.5M usd cerrados en ventas mientras vivo viajando
  </p>
  <h1
    class="text-white font-extrabold text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-[37px] max-w-[95%] sm:max-w-[90%] md:max-w-[790px] text-center mt-3 sm:mt-4 leading-[110%] sm:leading-[105%] md:leading-[100%] mx-auto px-4"
  >
    Si te gustaría trabajar desde tu casa, ganar en dólares y manejar tus
    propios horarios, esta
    <span class="relative italic inline-block">
      es tu oportunidad
      <svg
        class="absolute -bottom-[6px] left-0 w-full h-auto -z-10"
        width="314"
        height="11"
        viewBox="0 0 314 11"
        fill="none"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      >
        <path
          d="M0.999881 8.78845C205.765 -0.969132 259 3.00001 313.658 5.5327"
          stroke="url(#paint0_linear_18_15)"
          stroke-width="4"></path>
        <defs>
          <linearGradient
            id="paint0_linear_18_15"
            x1="1.05304"
            y1="4.34998"
            x2="313.628"
            y2="8.09373"
            gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
          >
            <stop stop-color="#F3D444"></stop>
            <stop offset="1" stop-color="#FFD200"></stop>
          </linearGradient>
        </defs>
      </svg>
    </span>
  </h1>
  <p
    class="leading-[120%] mt-3 sm:mt-4 mx-auto text-base md:text-[18px] text-center max-w-[90%] sm:max-w-[500px] text-white/80 px-4"
  >
    Genera ingresos constantes y disfruta de la <strong
      >libertad y flexibilidad de las ventas online.</strong
    >
  </p>

  <div class="open-form">
    <div
      class="mt-6 sm:mt-8 bgLinear cursor-pointer rounded-2xl sm:rounded-[18px] p-1 overflow-clip mx-auto max-w-[95%] sm:max-w-full w-full sm:w-[725px]"
    >
      <div
        class="p-2 sm:p-3 uppercase font-bold text-[#111] text-center text-base"
      >
        Mira el video y aprende como lo hacemos
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-gray-300 rounded-br-[14px] rounded-bl-[14px] w-full aspect-video"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
    <button
      class={`cursor-pointer flex gap-2 mt-6 items-center uppercase bgLinear w-fit font-semibold text-[#111] outline-4 outline-white/30 mx-auto py-3 sm:py-4 px-6 sm:px-8 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-[16px] text-base max-w-full sm:max-w-none`}
    >
      <span class="text-center">QUIERO VER COMO FUNCIONA</span>
      <svg
        width="13"
        height="12"
        viewBox="0 0 13 12"
        fill="none"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        class="flex-shrink-0"
      >
        <path
          d="M6.41318 11.6364L5.09499 10.3296L8.55522 6.86932H0.447266V4.94887H8.55522L5.09499 1.49432L6.41318 0.181824L12.1404 5.9091L6.41318 11.6364Z"
          fill="#111111"></path>
      </svg>
    </button>
  </div>

  <div class="calification-form hidden">
    <CalificationForm client:only="react" defaultEmail="" />
  </div>

  <div
    class="mt-6 sm:mt-8 mx-auto w-fit flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-2 items-center px-4"
  >
    <img
      src="/images/sales-mastery-profiles.png"
      alt="Sales Mastery Profiles"
      class="w-20 sm:w-auto"
    />
    <p
      class="text-white/80 max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-[220px] leading-[120%] text-center sm:text-left text-base"
    >
      +50 clientes ya superaron los USD 2.000 por mes
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
    const button = document.querySelector(".open-form");
    const form = document.querySelector(".calification-form");

    button?.addEventListener("click", () => {
      form?.classList.toggle("hidden");
    });
  });
</script>
